Checklist of common data cleansing tasks
-----------------------------------------

The checklist and R code included here is predominantly from the following course: https://www.linkedin.com/learning/cleaning-bad-data-in-r 

There is also another useful checklist from quartz here: https://github.com/quartz/bad-data-guide

Missing Data
  Missing values
  Missing Rows
  Aggregation and Missing Values

Duplicated Data
  Duplicated rows and values
  Aggregations

Formatting Data
  Dates
  Units
  Numbers as text
  Text as numbers
  Factors?
  Data Types
  Typos

Outliers
Illogical values
Tidy data
Common data problems
Suspicious values
Suspicious multiples
